# grapher_implicit_2x_smoke.numos — Phase 9E. Commit the BARE expression "2x"
# (no "y="), graph it, screenshot, and assert. Proves implicit-RHS + implicit
# multiplication together: the Tokenizer turns "2x" into "2*x"
# (Tokenizer::appendImplicitMulIfNeeded) and GraphModel::getExprRHS treats the
# missing '=' as y=<expr>, so "2x" plots y=2x (slope 2). Before 9E: no curve.
#
# Warning-only candidate (no golden blessed; the compare step warns when absent).
log "grapher_implicit_2x_smoke: waiting for launcher"
wait 200
open_app Grapher
wait 60
key down
key enter
key 2
key x
key enter
wait 80
key graph
wait 120
key ac
key 0
wait 180
screenshot out/grapher_implicit_2x_smoke.ppm
assert_app Grapher
log "grapher_implicit_2x_smoke: bare 2x plotted as y=2x"
